    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:6",
      "text": "Example Maya Scene（Maya 示例场景）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:8",
      "text": "要访问这些控件，请打开 Camera Attribute Editor，并在 RenderMan rollout 下选择 \"Enable Camera Projection\"",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:9",
      "text": "你会注意到 Camera Projection 字段为空。右键单击会出现两个选项：Omnidirectionalstereo（用于 VR 和类似应用）和 PxrCamera，请选择后者。",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 33
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:11",
      "text": "Field of View",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:12",
      "text": "与 Maya Camera 匹配，否则可能无法获得与 viewport 中相同的 framing。也可以在 camera editor 上选择 \"Use Camera Settings\"。",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:13",
      "text": "Tilt Angle：",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:15",
      "text": "Depth of Field in Maya",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:21",
      "text": "Roll Angle：",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:23",
      "text": "Focus Points：",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:26",
      "text": "创建一个 polygonal triangle（多边形三角形）。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:28",
      "text": "cluster handle",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:30",
      "text": "Animation Menu > Anim Deform > Open Full Deform Menu > Cluster",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:32",
      "text": "Create Menu > Locator",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:33",
      "text": "下创建一个 locator，并将它吸附到该顶点。将 cluster handle 作为 locator transform 的子级。现在移动 locator 就会移动 cluster 及其顶点。",
      "ascii_letters": 50,
      "cjk_chars": 32
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:35",
      "text": "Show Menu",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:37",
      "text": "Render Stats",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:39",
      "text": "现在你已经有办法看到对焦平面，需要将 locators（或 cluster handles）的 transform outputs 连接到",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:40",
      "text": "Focus Parameters",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:41",
      "text": "（用于 PxrCamera）。",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:42",
      "text": "从 Outliner 中选择 PxrCamera（可以通过在 Outliner Window 中",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:44",
      "text": "Display > DAG Object Only",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:46",
      "text": "将它和一个 locator transform 加载到 Connection Editor 中。将 Locator",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:47",
      "text": "Translate",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "619527435b:48",
      "text": "连接到每个 locator 对应的 PxrCamera",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
